  <entry>
    <title>Ubuntu20美化及DeepLearning配置</title>
    <link href="http://king-key.github.io/2021/01/22/Ubuntu20%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8ADeepLearning%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>http://king-key.github.io/2021/01/22/Ubuntu20%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8ADeepLearning%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2021-01-21T23:06:25.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-22T21:24:29.759Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>Ubuntu20.04系统美化&amp;深度学习环境的配置</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h3 id="1、Software"><a href="#1、Software" class="headerlink" title="1、Software"></a>1、Software</h3><ul><li><h4 id="typora"><a href="#typora" class="headerlink" title="typora"></a>typora</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget -qO - https://typora.io/linux/public-key.asc | sudo apt-key add -</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> add Typora<span class="string">&#x27;s repository</span></span></span><br><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository &#x27;deb https://typora.io/linux ./&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> install typora</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="sublime-text-and-sublime-merge"><a href="#sublime-text-and-sublime-merge" class="headerlink" title="sublime text and sublime merge"></a>sublime text and sublime merge</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget -qO - https://download.sublimetext.com/sublimehq-pub.gpg | sudo apt-key add -</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install apt-transport-https</span><br><span class="line">echo &quot;deb https://download.sublimetext.com/ apt/stable/&quot; | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/sublime-text.list</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install sublime-text</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install sublime-merge</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//注册码</span><br><span class="line">----- BEGIN LICENSE -----</span><br><span class="line">Member J2TeaM</span><br><span class="line">Single User License</span><br><span class="line">EA7E-1011316</span><br><span class="line">D7DA350E 1B8B0760 972F8B60 F3E64036</span><br><span class="line">B9B4E234 F356F38F 0AD1E3B7 0E9C5FAD</span><br><span class="line">FA0A2ABE 25F65BD8 D51458E5 3923CE80</span><br><span class="line">87428428 79079A01 AA69F319 A1AF29A4</span><br><span class="line">A684C2DC 0B1583D4 19CBD290 217618CD</span><br><span class="line">5653E0A0 BACE3948 BB2EE45E 422D2C87</span><br><span class="line">DD9AF44B 99C49590 D2DBDEE1 75860FD2</span><br><span class="line">8C8BB2AD B2ECE5A4 EFC08AF2 25A9B864</span><br><span class="line">------ END LICENSE ------​</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="Clion"><a href="#Clion" class="headerlink" title="Clion"></a>Clion</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo snap install clion --classic</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//if error</span><br><span class="line">sudo snap changes</span><br><span class="line">sudo snap aborts ID</span><br><span class="line">sudo snap install clion --classic</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//注册码</span><br><span class="line">https://shimo.im/docs/XvW3WpHgHdRHVXgV/read</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、DeepLearning"><a href="#2、DeepLearning" class="headerlink" title="2、DeepLearning"></a>2、DeepLearning</h3><ul><li><h4 id="cuda-11-0"><a href="#cuda-11-0" class="headerlink" title="cuda 11.0"></a>cuda 11.0</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ./cuda_11.0.2_450.51.05_linux.run</span><br><span class="line">nvcc -V</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> add path <span class="keyword">in</span> .zshrc</span></span><br><span class="line">export CUDA_HOME=/usr/local/cuda-11.0</span><br><span class="line">export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$&#123;CUDA_HOME&#125;/lib64</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=$&#123;CUDA_HOME&#125;/bin:$PATH</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sourch .zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="cudnn-18-0"><a href="#cudnn-18-0" class="headerlink" title="cudnn 18.0"></a>cudnn 18.0</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo cp cuda/include/cudnn.h /usr/local/cuda-11.0/include</span><br><span class="line">sudo cp cuda/lib64/libcudnn* /usr/local/cuda-11.0/lib64</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod a+r /usr/local/cuda-11.0/lib64/libcudnn*</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod a+r /usr/local/cuda-11.0/include/cudnn.h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="TensorFlow-GPU-2-4"><a href="#TensorFlow-GPU-2-4" class="headerlink" title="TensorFlow-GPU 2.4"></a>TensorFlow-GPU 2.4</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install tensorflow-gpu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//test cpu</span><br><span class="line">import tensorflow as tf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;TensorFlow version:&quot;,tf.__version__)</span><br><span class="line">tf.compat.v1.disable_eager_execution() </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">with tf.device(&#x27;/cpu:0&#x27;):</span><br><span class="line">    a=tf.constant([1.0,2.0,3.0],shape=[3],name=&#x27;a&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">    b=tf.constant([1.0,2.0,3.0],shape=[3],name=&#x27;b&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">with tf.device(&#x27;/gpu:0&#x27;):</span><br><span class="line">    c = a + b</span><br><span class="line">sess=tf.compat.v1.Session(config=tf.compat.v1.ConfigProto(log_device_placement=True))</span><br><span class="line">print(sess.run(c))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="PyTorch-GPU-1-8"><a href="#PyTorch-GPU-1-8" class="headerlink" title="PyTorch-GPU 1.8"></a>PyTorch-GPU 1.8</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install numpy</span><br><span class="line">pip install --pre torch torchvision torchaudio -f https://download.pytorch.org/whl/nightly/cu110/torch_nightly.html</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//test gpu</span><br><span class="line">import torch</span><br><span class="line">print(torch.cuda.is_available())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="OpenCV-4-5"><a href="#OpenCV-4-5" class="headerlink" title="OpenCV 4.5"></a>OpenCV 4.5</h4></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/opencv/opencv/archive/4.5.1.zip</span><br><span class="line">unzip opencv-4.5.1.zip</span><br><span class="line">cd opencv-4.5.1</span><br><span class="line">mkdir build</span><br><span class="line">cd build</span><br><span class="line">cmake ..</span><br><span class="line">make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><h4 id="Other-App"><a href="#Other-App" class="headerlink" title="Other App"></a>Other App</h4><h5 id="streamlit"><a href="#streamlit" class="headerlink" title="streamlit"></a><a href="https://www.streamlit.io/">streamlit</a></h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install streamlit //create web AI app</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="pqi"><a href="#pqi" class="headerlink" title="pqi"></a><a href="https://pypi.org/project/pqi/">pqi</a></h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install pqi //change pip channels</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、Shell"><a href="#3、Shell" class="headerlink" title="3、Shell"></a>3、Shell</h3></li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//install zsh</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install zsh</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//install oh-my-zsh</span><br><span class="line">//copy install.sh https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/blob/master/tools/install.sh</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod a+r install.sh </span><br><span class="line">./install.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//themes</span><br><span class="line">ZSH_THEME=&quot;ys&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//plugins</span><br><span class="line">sudo git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git .oh-my-zsh/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line">plugins=(</span><br><span class="line">git </span><br><span class="line">//add</span><br><span class="line">web-search  //命令行直接搜索</span><br><span class="line">zsh-syntax-highlighting //高亮</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//other </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install tree</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install htop</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install tmux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/2021/01/22/Ubuntu20%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8ADeepLearning%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Screenshot%20from%202021-01-17%2012-31-36.png" alt="Screenshot from 2021-01-17 12-31-36"></p><p><img src="/2021/01/22/Ubuntu20%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8ADeepLearning%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/Screenshot%20from%202021-01-17%2012-35-31.png" alt="Screenshot from 2021-01-17 12-35-31"></p>]]></content>
    
    
